    <h4>
      A MAZE. / Berlin is the annual arthouse games and playful media festival. A MAZE. / Berlin invites the globally diverse experimental and independent games and playful media scene to also explore the works 
of worldbuilders, digital artists, hybrid performers, virtual musicians, immersive theater and more playful creatives to Berlin: with the goal to connect, to present and experience other works at the most inspiring festival on that behalf including talks, conversations, playformances and workshops – we are celebrating the new wave of video games making.
